  "texts": [
    "As previously mentioned, comorbidity with other SLDs is likely to occur.",
    "Since their presence could bias the answers, students that have a certificate of the simultaneous presence of SLDs other than dyslexia have been discarded.",
    "Dyscalculia and Dysgraphia will be, singularly, the object of other two similar studies.",
    "Handling the three disorders singularly should avoid biases and provide more targeted results.",
    "The collection of the data, as well as all the experimental protocols employed in this research were subjected to a double conformity check."
